name: sample

prompt_map.0: Imagine a surrealist art piece of an girl, where dreamlike imagery and illogical scenes challenge the viewer's sense of reality. The girl is placed in an unexpected context or combined with other disparate elements, creating a sense of mystery and intrigue. The colors are often vivid or unsettling, contributing to the surreal quality of the artwork. This style plays with the subconscious, drawing on dream imagery and symbolic content to evoke emotional responses. The composition is often whimsical or disturbing, bending the rules of logic and reality. The girl is not just depicted; it's transformed into a piece of the surreal landscape, inviting the viewer to explore a world where the ordinary becomes extraordinary, and the impossible seems plausible.

n_prompt: 2D, flat, ugly, blurry, distorted, grainy, static, noisy, deformed, shaky, abrupt, flat, low contrast, nude, nsfw, oversaturated, underexposed, sketch, watercolor
